          &#9760; If your answer is wrong you get terminated from the quiz.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- creating a modal for when quiz ends -->
    <div class="winings-box" id="end-box">
      <div class="winings-details">
        <h1>Congratulations, Game Completed.</h1>

        <div class="winings">
          <p>Amount Won : <span id="final-amount"></span> Rupees</p>
        </div>
        <div class="winings">
